{"tid":1762441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（抵制TVB）跳船最後機會 12/12前不回應將永不錄用","createTime":"2019-11-29T15:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T07:00:47.000Z","uid":75759,"like":121,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"538a4b5cc86ba0e044e4d577e2fe5ed1a5df79a1","tid":1762441,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:00:43.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n<br />\n死線前不回應TVB廣告事宜將視為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">表態支持CCTVB假新聞</span></strong></span>，並可榮登<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>CCTVB廣告制裁名單永遠榮譽商戶</strong></span></span>，限期後即使聯絡團隊亦將不予除名，香港人會知道如何消費。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EocSuUt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEocSuUt.jpg&h=0708f27d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如 貴司現尚有TVB廣告，建議 貴司檢視以下和解方案，並於限期前作實際行動，以免無辜遭受與TVB攬炒之禍：<br />\n<br />\n一、<br />\n開誠佈公，讓市民大眾得悉 貴司與TVB廣告合約詳情，並澄清 貴司是否仍與TVB簽訂2020廣告合約，以免市民誤會<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong> 貴司與TVB狼狽為奸、淪為抹黑打壓港人爭取合法合理民主訴求的幫凶</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n二、<br />\n私訊我方團隊，清楚說明 貴司與TVB之合作關係、以及於TVB旗下平台投放廣告之意向。相關申報經團隊確認後自當將 貴司從制裁名單除名，亦可免去受鄰國玻璃心攻擊之麻煩，一舉兩得。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ccym7FT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCcym7FT.jpg&h=0f37aec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n誠如閣下所見，香港人一直爭取的五大訴求具民意基礎。若 貴司仍決意站於高牆的一方、支持黨媒喉舌<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以不實報導污名化香港市民的民主運動</span></strong>，香港市民將以實際抵制行動回應， <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>貴司恐成商界的新民黨</strong></span>。TVB這公信力全無之機構實在不值一顧，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">於TVB旗下平台投放廣告絕對難收宣傳預期之效，反而有損 貴司的形象以致市場收益</span></strong>，懇請三思。"},{"pid":"77cd88fcb167f24b82025248886df62cf7a22d06","tid":1762441,"uid":75759,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:00:55.000Z","msg":"【終極任務⚔️50大廣告商】<br />\n [Misson 4 of 14]<br />\n<br />\n倒數13日, 大家幫幫手炸爆CCTVB個老X!! 😡<br />\nP.S.呢三間都係屬於[利潔時]集團, 俾咗好多錢俾CCTVB!! 🤯<br />\n<br />\n💎是日精選廣告商: (3/50間) <br />\n1️⃣使立消<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/StrepsilsHongKong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FStrepsilsHongKong%2F&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=b01f98f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/StrepsilsHongKong/</a><br />\n<br />\n2️⃣滴露 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dettolhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdettolhk%2F&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=37bc893b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dettolhk/</a><br />\n<br />\n3️⃣Schiff<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Schiff.MoveFreeHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSchiff.MoveFreeHK%2F&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=61df389d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Schiff.MoveFreeHK/</a><br />\n <br />\n留言範本<br />\n💢要全力阻止簽訂2020合約💢<br />\n歡迎創意修改：<br />\n無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。<br />\n圖片link：<a href=\"http://na.cx/i/1u619D6.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1u619D6.png&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=d18e5213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://na.cx/i/1u619D6.png</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pm6v02q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPm6v02q.jpg&h=de273553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n📮一次過Send Email最有效!!📮<br />\n📤電郵清單及範本📥<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1yd6UZJPyqx8YOIB7feA2_UWx7071CqaFuPgxDw1OeoM/edit?fbclid=IwAR1SNGbTxPzzIFWWT3GPWcfTON1yEsJUY7REve2V0jnRLQia5RxakOZBvzA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1yd6UZJPyqx8YOIB7feA2_UWx7071CqaFuPgxDw1OeoM%2Fedit%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1SNGbTxPzzIFWWT3GPWcfTON1yEsJUY7REve2V0jnRLQia5RxakOZBvzA&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=e5ff9c09\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1yd6UZJPyqx8YOIB7feA2_UWx7071CqaFuPgxDw1OeoM/edit?fbclid=IwAR1SNGbTxPzzIFWWT3GPWcfTON1yEsJUY7REve2V0jnRLQia5RxakOZBvzA</a><br />\n<br />\n⚔️補做/一次過做任務⚔️<br />\n👇50大廣告商任務時間表<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1nyLgh1WNRNQz7duhC6VRNV3FxNG0F7SHLhtZ6n5bN64/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1nyLgh1WNRNQz7duhC6VRNV3FxNG0F7SHLhtZ6n5bN64%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=dfa601a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1nyLgh1WNRNQz7duhC6VRNV3FxNG0F7SHLhtZ6n5bN64/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"d96893c5d82125a5b0a01be436476e1a36b4fc9f","tid":1762441,"uid":75759,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:07:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yuq1oiu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYuq1oiu.jpg&h=19afe123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTVB廣告商11月號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f027295f4de7d54175e729f1b3a9a8432160d62","tid":1762441,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:07:47.000Z","msg":"推左先"},{"pid":"1300493bb0d8f31d60b3c1474eec68af00763593","tid":1762441,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:07:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59afef3955488fc33841df811d1c6158cd21ae8e","tid":1762441,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a82e8e30a1c536361a0c9f08594c7fe003e8717","tid":1762441,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20