":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T07:42:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"410c04df0696e26493cc370d02c993b82b06c258","tid":1762441,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T07:44:21.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"dfed1de315796abf21c7f95967c876d24b09d345","tid":1762441,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T07:55:44.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ddbc8eee4a9a882d684a5c628df76a3f4bca2ba","tid":1762441,"uid":138774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T07:58:44.000Z","msg":"推爆佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c6eceb7405083b876c276953f2b7f07aee28a8e","tid":1762441,"uid":101906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:04:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"08d651e4d30e01235143cf2cc24e053a79913692","tid":1762441,"uid":133383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:13:12.000Z","msg":"support <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef5f59809bfad03d89c91d06283fabd4e12fd242","tid":1762441,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"538a4b5cc86ba0e044e4d577e2fe5ed1a5df79a1","tid":1762441,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:00:43.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n<br />\n死線前不回應TVB廣告事宜將視為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">表態支持CCTVB假新聞</span></strong></span>，並可榮登<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>CCTVB廣告制裁名單永遠榮譽商戶</strong></span></span>，限期後即使聯絡團隊亦將不予除名，香港人會知道如何消費。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EocSuUt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEocSuUt.jpg&h=0708f27d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如 貴司現尚有TVB廣告，建議 貴司檢視以下和解方案，並於限期前作實際行動，以免無辜遭受與TVB攬炒之禍：<br />\n<br />\n一、<br />\n開誠佈公，讓市民大眾得悉 貴司與TVB廣告合約詳情，並澄清 貴司是否仍與TVB簽訂2020廣告合約，以免市民誤會<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong> 貴司與TVB狼狽為奸、淪為抹黑打壓港人爭取合法合理民主訴求的幫凶</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n二、<br />\n私訊我方團隊，清楚說明 貴司與TVB之合作關係、以及於TVB旗下平台投放廣告之意向。相關申報經團隊確認後自當將 貴司從制裁名單除名，亦可免去受鄰國玻璃心攻擊之麻煩，一舉兩得。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ccym7FT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCcym7FT.jpg&h=0f37aec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n誠如閣下所見，香港人一直爭取的五大訴求具民意基礎。若 貴司仍決意站於高牆的一方、支持黨媒喉舌<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以不實報導污名化香港市民的民主運動</span></strong>，香港市民將以實際抵制行動回應， <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>貴司恐成商界的新民黨</strong></span>。TVB這公信力全無之機構實在不值一顧，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">於TVB旗下平台投放廣告絕對難收宣傳預期之效，反而有損 貴司的形象以致市場收益</span></strong>，懇請三思。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:15:13.000Z","msg":"用敝人係咪謙讓過本人？"},{"pid":"89887192cc027e866ee4399434045b90974771ff","tid":1762441,"uid":8125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:15:40.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5347e864e4fa2bf6553a67d4d284d6a4ebac39a0","tid":1762441,"uid":164190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:25:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"140336d2b5f9a04b69dd034a95668abd9f6f5720","tid":1762441,"uid":41629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:31:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d6ba0855d0c3a79b4cda2c5dda6c680583d7509","tid":1762441,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T19:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hk