" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPm6v02q.jpg&h=de273553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n📮一次過Send Email最有效!!📮<br />\n📤電郵清單及範本📥<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1yd6UZJPyqx8YOIB7feA2_UWx7071CqaFuPgxDw1OeoM/edit?fbclid=IwAR1SNGbTxPzzIFWWT3GPWcfTON1yEsJUY7REve2V0jnRLQia5RxakOZBvzA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1yd6UZJPyqx8YOIB7feA2_UWx7071CqaFuPgxDw1OeoM%2Fedit%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1SNGbTxPzzIFWWT3GPWcfTON1yEsJUY7REve2V0jnRLQia5RxakOZBvzA&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=e5ff9c09\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1yd6UZJPyqx8YOIB7feA2_UWx7071CqaFuPgxDw1OeoM/edit?fbclid=IwAR1SNGbTxPzzIFWWT3GPWcfTON1yEsJUY7REve2V0jnRLQia5RxakOZBvzA</a><br />\n<br />\n⚔️補做/一次過做任務⚔️<br />\n👇50大廣告商任務時間表<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1nyLgh1WNRNQz7duhC6VRNV3FxNG0F7SHLhtZ6n5bN64/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1nyLgh1WNRNQz7duhC6VRNV3FxNG0F7SHLhtZ6n5bN64%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=dfa601a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1nyLgh1WNRNQz7duhC6VRNV3FxNG0F7SHLhtZ6n5bN64/edit?usp=sharing</a>"}}